WEBVTT

00:01.500 --> 00:05.104
I AM PLACING THIS RECORDER
IN THE CLOSET.

00:06.191 --> 00:07.138
ADAM?

00:07.173 --> 00:09.041
I'M SORRY.
DID SOMETHING JUST TOUCH YOU?

00:09.076 --> 00:10.908
YES!

00:10.943 --> 00:13.812
MY UNCLE
WAS MURDERED IN HERE.

00:13.813 --> 00:18.684
I SAW A MAN STANDING
RIGHT HERE IN MY ROOM.

00:18.719 --> 00:21.221
IS THERE ANYBODY
DOWN THERE?

00:23.789 --> 00:26.958
MY DAUGHTER HAD
THE HOUSE BLESSED.

00:26.993 --> 00:30.630
BUT I FELT LIKE THERE
WAS SOME EVIL LEFT BEHIND.

00:30.665 --> 00:32.165
MY GOD!

00:36.235 --> 00:38.002
I'M AMY BRUNI.

00:38.037 --> 00:40.438
AND I'M ADAM BERRY.

00:40.473 --> 00:42.506
WE'VE SPENT
A COMBINED 30 YEARS

00:42.541 --> 00:46.144
INVESTIGATING THE WORLD'S
MOST TERRIFYING HAUNTINGS.

00:46.145 --> 00:47.779
AFTER THOUSANDS OF CASES,

00:47.814 --> 00:51.050
WE ARE READY FOR OUR
MOST IMPORTANT JOURNEY YET.

00:52.986 --> 00:57.123
RESCUING FAMILIES TERRORIZED
BY PARANORMAL ACTIVITY

00:57.158 --> 01:00.025
IN THEIR OWN HOMES.

01:00.026 --> 01:02.862
WE UNCOVER THE TRUTH
BEHIND THE HAUNTING

01:02.897 --> 01:05.698
TO HELP FAMILIES
RECLAIM THEIR HOMES...

01:05.733 --> 01:07.217
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

01:07.252 --> 01:08.666
...AND THEIR LIVES.

01:08.701 --> 01:11.738
CAPTIONS PAID FOR BY
DISCOVERY COMMUNICATIONS

01:13.339 --> 01:15.506
<i>Good evening.</i>

01:15.541 --> 01:17.843
<i> So, I'm messaging on behalf
of my mother, Linda.</i>

01:17.878 --> 01:19.844
<i> She lives in Chelsea,
Massachusetts.</i>

01:19.879 --> 01:23.549
<i> And her house
is most definitely haunted.</i>

01:23.584 --> 01:24.915
<i> She's the victim
of shadow figures,</i>

01:24.950 --> 01:27.670
<i> and she will never go down
in the basement.</i>

01:27.705 --> 01:30.355
<i> She's lived there
for more than 35 years,</i>

01:30.390 --> 01:33.559
<i> and it's the house where
she raised her five kids.</i>

01:33.594 --> 01:36.729
<i> My Uncle Eric was actually
murdered in the house,</i>

01:36.764 --> 01:38.762
<i> in one of the apartments
downstairs.</i>

01:38.797 --> 01:41.734
<i> We don't know if it's him
or something else in the house.</i>

01:41.769 --> 01:43.601
<i> Please, come check
out the house.</i>

01:43.602 --> 01:44.569
THAT'S A LOT.

01:44.604 --> 01:45.569
I KNOW.
IT'S A LOT.

01:45.604 --> 01:47.471
AND THAT'S
JUST THE BEGINNING.

01:47.506 --> 01:50.442
THIS CASE, ALMOST MORE THAN
ANY OTHER CASE WE'VE DONE,

01:50.477 --> 01:52.211
I JUST FEEL LIKE WE HAVE
A LOT RIDING ON IT.

01:52.246 --> 01:53.277
WOW.

01:53.312 --> 01:54.646
THE BROTHER'S MURDERED
IN THE BASEMENT?

01:54.647 --> 01:55.897
YEAH, THE BROTHER.

01:55.932 --> 01:57.148
WHEN DID THAT HAPPEN?

01:57.149 --> 02:01.320
THE MURDER IN THE BASEMENT
TOOK PLACE IN, I BELIEVE, 1995.

02:01.355 --> 02:04.188
HER BROTHER ERIC,
WHO WAS MENTALLY HANDICAPPED,

02:04.223 --> 02:07.960
HAD THE BRAIN CAPACITY OF
LIKE A 10- OR 12-YEAR-OLD,

02:07.995 --> 02:10.759
WAS MURDERED
BY HIS OWN BROTHER.

02:10.794 --> 02:15.001
SHE'S LIKE, "YOU GUYS ARE KINDA
MY ONLY HOPE AT THIS POINT."

02:19.072 --> 02:21.338
THIS IS GONNA BE A TOUGH CASE.

02:21.373 --> 02:23.875
WE'RE DEALING WITH A HOME
THAT'S HAD PARANORMAL ACTIVITY

02:23.876 --> 02:25.877
FOR MORE THAN 35 YEARS,

02:25.912 --> 02:28.314
SOME OF WHICH MAY BE LINKED
TO A TRAGIC MURDER.

02:28.349 --> 02:30.382
SO THE EMOTIONAL TIES RUN DEEP,

02:30.383 --> 02:32.150
BUT WE'RE GONNA DO
WHATEVER IT TAKES

02:32.185 --> 02:33.918
TO DETERMINE
WHAT SPIRIT OR SPIRITS

02:33.919 --> 02:35.319
ARE SCARING THE FAMILY

02:35.354 --> 02:38.290
AND HOPEFULLY HELP THEM
OVERCOME THEIR FEARS.

02:38.325 --> 02:39.523
YOUR HOUSE IS GORGEOUS.

02:39.558 --> 02:41.994
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.
THIS IS MY DAUGHTER SANDY.

02:42.029 --> 02:43.094
HI.

02:43.129 --> 02:44.530
SO HOW LONG
HAVE YOU BEEN HERE?

02:44.565 --> 02:46.397
UM, SINCE '74.

02:46.432 --> 02:48.550
MY GOODNESS.
SO A WHILE.

02:48.585 --> 02:50.634
I KNOW
YOU GUYS CONTACTED US.

02:50.669 --> 02:54.473
AND IT SOUNDS LIKE YOU
HAVE A LOT GOING ON HERE.

02:54.508 --> 02:56.793
A LOT OF STRANGE THINGS
HAVE HAPPENED

02:56.828 --> 02:59.078
AFTER WE HAD
SOME DEATHS IN THE FAMILY,

02:59.113 --> 03:00.578
EVEN PRIOR TO THAT.

03:00.613 --> 03:02.048
EVEN PRIOR.
YEAH, WHEN WE FIRST --

03:02.083 --> 03:03.448
WHEN I FIRST
BOUGHT THE HOUSE.

03:03.483 --> 03:06.686
SO ACTIVITY HAPPENED
BEFORE YOUR BROTHER PASSED.

03:06.721 --> 03:08.421
IT WAS CONSTANTLY
THINGS HAPPENING.

03:08.456 --> 03:09.689
IT'S GETTING
TO A POINT NOW

03:09.724 --> 03:10.888
IT'S AN EVERYDAY
OCCURRENCE.

03:10.923 --> 03:13.426
SOMETHING HAPPENED
THIS WEEK, TOO.

03:13.461 --> 03:16.761
MY HUSBAND
WOULD SEE SHADOWS

03:16.796 --> 03:19.332
WALKING FROM ONE BEDROOM
TO ANOTHER.

03:20.799 --> 03:23.736
ABOUT THREE, FOUR WEEKS AGO,
I WAS SLEEPING.

03:23.771 --> 03:26.272
SOMETHING WOKE ME UP,
LIKE, SOMETHING

03:26.307 --> 03:27.672
THAT WASN'T NORMAL.

03:27.707 --> 03:31.110
MY HUSBAND
CAME INTO THE BEDROOM

03:31.145 --> 03:34.514
AND SAW SOMEONE
TALL STAND OVER ME

03:34.549 --> 03:37.614
AND TOUCH MY FACE.

03:37.649 --> 03:41.287
SO THAT'S WHEN
I REALLY GOT SCARED.

03:41.322 --> 03:42.520
I JUST NEED TO KNOW

03:42.555 --> 03:45.290
FOR MY OWN PEACE OF MIND
AND FOR MY CHILDREN.

03:45.325 --> 03:47.524
I JUST NEED TO KNOW.

03:47.559 --> 03:49.628
I'M THINKING MAYBE
WE COULD HEAD DOWNSTAIRS.

03:49.663 --> 03:51.697
IF YOU DON'T MIND,
SANDY WILL TAKE YOU DOWN.

03:51.732 --> 03:53.699
YOU DON'T GO
DOWNSTAIRS AT ALL?

03:53.734 --> 03:56.333
NO.

03:58.637 --> 04:01.274
WHEN I'M AT THE TOP
OF THE STAIRS,

04:01.309 --> 04:03.941
I JUST GET THIS STRANGE

04:03.976 --> 04:05.778
ALMOST LIKE
ANXIETY ATTACK.

04:05.813 --> 04:07.077
YEAH.

04:07.112 --> 04:09.214
DO YOU THINK THERE'S
SOMETHING DOWN IN THE BASEMENT?

04:09.249 --> 04:10.548
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT I'M SAYING?

04:10.583 --> 04:11.851
I FEEL LIKE
THERE'S SOMEBODY THERE.

04:11.886 --> 04:13.453
JUST DOESN'T
FEEL COMFORTABLE.

04:13.488 --> 04:15.688
NOT AT ALL.

04:18.958 --> 04:20.826
SEEING YOUR MOM'S
REACTION TO THAT,

04:20.861 --> 04:22.860
HOW DOES THAT
MAKE YOU FEEL?

04:22.895 --> 04:24.496
AFTER MY UNCLE WAS KILLED,
I BEGGED HER

04:24.497 --> 04:26.030
TO SELL THE HOUSE
AND MOVE.

04:26.065 --> 04:28.467
BUT SHE JUST HAD SUCH
A CONNECTION HERE.

04:28.502 --> 04:29.867
AND SHE JUST FELT LIKE,
YOU KNOW,

04:29.902 --> 04:32.003
"I'M NOT GONNA HAVE SOMEBODY
PUSH ME OUT OF MY HOME."

04:32.004 --> 04:33.203
RIGHT, RIGHT.

04:33.238 --> 04:36.476
AND TO SEE HER NOT
WANNA COME DOWN HERE, IT IS SAD.

04:38.077 --> 04:39.410
WHAT HAS HAPPENED
DOWN HERE?

04:39.445 --> 04:41.746
ONE NIGHT, I WAS
SLEEPING ON THIS COUCH.

04:41.781 --> 04:44.150
AND SOMETHING WOKE ME UP
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE NIGHT.

04:44.185 --> 04:45.885
AND I LOOKED OVER
IN THAT DIRECTION.

04:45.920 --> 04:47.586
AND I SAW SOMEBODY
STANDING THERE,

04:47.621 --> 04:48.953
LOOKED LIKE AN OUTLINE.

04:48.988 --> 04:51.257
AND I ORIGINALLY HAD THOUGHT,
"MY GOD.

04:51.292 --> 04:52.557
SOMEONE BROKE IN,
AND I CAUGHT THEM.

04:52.592 --> 04:55.693
SOMEONE'S IN THE HOUSE,"
BECAUSE IT WAS THAT CLEAR.

04:55.694 --> 04:58.731
SO I DOVE OVER THE COUCH.
AND I HIT THE LIGHT SWITCH HERE.

04:58.766 --> 05:01.501
AND THE LIGHTS CAME ON,
AND NOBODY WAS THERE.

05:01.536 --> 05:02.499
MY GOODNESS.

05:02.534 --> 05:04.236
YEAH, SO THAT WAS
A LITTLE WEIRD.

05:04.237 --> 05:05.569
SO THIS IS
THE FAMILY ROOM.

05:05.604 --> 05:07.072
AND THERE'S ANOTHER
APARTMENT THIS WAY?

05:07.107 --> 05:09.575
- CORRECT.
- OKAY.

05:11.677 --> 05:13.245
A LITTLE BACK STORY
ON THIS APARTMENT,

05:13.280 --> 05:15.079
MY UNCLE LIVED HERE.

05:15.114 --> 05:18.282
MY UNCLE WAS BORN WITH
CEREBRAL PALSY AND EPILEPSY.

05:18.283 --> 05:21.336
AND HE ALSO
LOST OXYGEN AT BIRTH,

05:21.371 --> 05:23.781
SO HE WAS
DEVELOPMENTALLY BEHIND.

05:23.816 --> 05:25.955
HE WAS 33.
BUT HE ALMOST WAS,

05:25.990 --> 05:28.094
LIKE, THE AGE
OF A 12-YEAR-OLD.

05:28.129 --> 05:29.927
HIS NAME WAS ERIC.

05:29.962 --> 05:32.196
AND HE WAS MURDERED
IN HERE.

05:32.231 --> 05:35.334
ACTUALLY, RIGHT THERE
IN FRONT OF THE DOOR

05:35.369 --> 05:37.202
WAS WHERE HIS BODY
WAS LEFT.

05:38.470 --> 05:40.371
WHAT HAPPENED?

05:40.406 --> 05:43.109
THERE WAS A DISAGREEMENT
WITH HIS BROTHER,

05:43.144 --> 05:45.796
MY OTHER UNCLE,
WHO HAD DRUG ISSUES.

05:45.831 --> 05:48.424
HE WAS BREAKING
INTO MY MOTHER'S HOUSE,

05:48.459 --> 05:50.982
AND THERE WAS A FIGHT,
AND HE KILLED HIM.

05:51.017 --> 05:54.787
SO SINCE THEN, I GUESS,
WHAT ACTIVITY HAS HAPPENED?

05:54.822 --> 05:56.086
MY DAUGHTER
LIVED DOWN HERE

05:56.121 --> 05:58.091
WITH HER DAUGHTER,
ARIANNA, MY GRANDDAUGHTER.

05:58.126 --> 06:00.024
AND THERE WERE ALWAYS
THINGS HAPPENING.

06:00.059 --> 06:02.128
LIKE, SHE WOULD ALWAYS STAND
AT THE EDGE OF HER CRIB,

06:02.163 --> 06:04.163
FACING THIS WAY
AND LOOK RIGHT AT THE CLOSET.

06:04.198 --> 06:07.499
AND SHE SAW A SHADOW.

06:07.534 --> 06:08.499
WEIRD.

06:08.534 --> 06:11.153
SHE CLEARLY REMEMBERS
IT TO THIS DAY.

06:11.188 --> 06:13.737
THAT'S WHEN I STARTED
TO WORRY A LITTLE.

06:13.772 --> 06:16.174
AND THEY ENDED UP
MOVING BACK HOME WITH ME, SO...

06:16.209 --> 06:17.107
- YEAH.
- RIGHT.

06:17.142 --> 06:18.409
IS THAT WHY
THEY MOVED BACK?

06:18.444 --> 06:21.080
YEAH, SHE WAS JUST --
IT WAS KIND OF LIKE, ENOUGH.

06:21.115 --> 06:23.383
AND SHE WAS JUST
LIKE, BOOM, HOME.

06:25.718 --> 06:27.618
AFTER TALKING WITH SANDY,
IT SOUNDED LIKE

06:27.653 --> 06:31.057
A LOT OF MEMBERS OF THE FAMILY
HAD EXPERIENCES IN THE BASEMENT.

06:31.092 --> 06:32.991
SO I WANT TO SIT DOWN
WITH HER DAUGHTERS,

06:33.026 --> 06:34.725
ADISON AND HADLEY,
AND FIND OUT

06:34.760 --> 06:36.729
IF THEY'VE EVER HAD
ANY EXPERIENCES THERE.

06:37.830 --> 06:40.466
THANK YOU FOR SITTING
WITH ME FOR A LITTLE BIT.

06:40.501 --> 06:43.603
SO, AS CHILDREN,
WHEN WAS THE FIRST TIME

06:43.638 --> 06:46.670
YOU EACH HAD AN EXPERIENCE
IN THE HOUSE?

06:46.705 --> 06:50.542
ONE TIME, I WAS DOWN HERE,
AND MY GRANDMOTHER SENT ME

06:50.577 --> 06:52.477
DOWN TO THE OTHER FRIDGE
OVER THERE

06:52.478 --> 06:54.613
JUST TO GET SOMETHING SIMPLE,
WHATEVER WE NEEDED,

06:54.648 --> 06:55.946
MILK OR WHATEVER IT WAS.

06:55.981 --> 06:57.147
THE WAY
THAT THE STAIRS ARE,

06:57.182 --> 06:59.184
YOU CAN SEE DOWN HERE
UNTIL THE LAST SECOND.

06:59.219 --> 07:01.287
ONE TIME, I HAPPENED
TO LOOK TO THE RIGHT,

07:01.322 --> 07:03.320
LOOKED BACK TO THE LEFT,
AND I CAN DESCRIBE

07:03.355 --> 07:07.093
TO YOU COMPLETELY A SIDE PROFILE
OF A MAN WALKING.

07:09.929 --> 07:12.196
AND I REMEMBER
THE WAY HE WALKED WAS

07:12.197 --> 07:14.733
JUST SUBTLE AND LIKE HE DIDN'T
HAVE A CARE IN THE WORLD.

07:14.768 --> 07:16.634
JUST WALKED
RIGHT DOWN HERE.

07:16.669 --> 07:19.570
I WATCHED THE ENTIRE THING
FOR PROBABLY LIKE FOUR SECONDS,

07:19.571 --> 07:20.939
AND THEN I SPRINTED
UP THE STAIRS

07:20.974 --> 07:22.508
TO MY GRANDMOTHER CRYING.

07:22.543 --> 07:23.741
SO, HOW ABOUT YOU?

07:23.742 --> 07:25.311
WHAT WAS YOUR FIRST PARANORMAL
EXPERIENCE IN THE HOUSE?

07:25.346 --> 07:28.579
SO, I NEVER HAD
ANYTHING AS VIVID AS THAT.

07:28.614 --> 07:30.949
A LOT OF IT WAS SILHOUETTES,
WHICH WE'VE ALL SAID

07:30.984 --> 07:33.284
THAT WE'VE SEEN A FEW
OF THOSE HERE AND THERE.

07:33.285 --> 07:36.320
AND IT'S BEEN DOWN HERE,
NEVER --

07:36.355 --> 07:37.857
YOU NEVER WANT TO COME
IN THE BASEMENT ALONE.

07:37.892 --> 07:39.190
IT WAS ALWAYS A KNOWN THING.

07:39.225 --> 07:43.295
AND IT SOUNDS SO SILLY,
BUT YOU COULD REALLY JUST FEEL

07:43.330 --> 07:45.296
THAT I WAS NOT
THE ONLY ONE HERE.

07:45.331 --> 07:48.667
WHAT WOULD BE
THE BEST OUTCOME FOR YOU GUYS

07:48.702 --> 07:50.667
AFTER WE'RE DONE
WITH ALL OF THIS?

07:50.702 --> 07:53.922
I WANT WHAT HAS HAPPENED TO US
TO HAPPEN.

07:53.957 --> 07:57.143
I WANT, LIKE, SOMEONE
OUTSIDE OF THE FAMILY

07:57.178 --> 07:58.945
TO WITNESS
WHAT WE WITNESS.

07:58.980 --> 08:01.364
- RIGHT.
- YEAH, SOME VALIDATION

08:01.399 --> 08:03.748
WOULD DEFINITELY
BE HELPFUL.

08:03.749 --> 08:06.151
I MEAN, THE MAIN GOAL IS
TO BE ABLE TO HAVE EVERYONE

08:06.186 --> 08:07.587
THAT LIVES HERE
AND HAS BEEN HERE

08:07.622 --> 08:08.953
TO BE COMFORTABLE
IN THIS BASEMENT,

08:08.988 --> 08:11.657
NOT, YOU KNOW, HAVE
TO RUN IN AND RUN OUT.

08:11.692 --> 08:12.657
RIGHT.

08:16.762 --> 08:20.198
THIS CASE CARRIES MORE
EMOTIONAL BAGGAGE THAN MOST,

08:20.233 --> 08:23.635
SO WE'RE GONNA DO WHATEVER WE
CAN TO FIND ANSWERS FOR LINDA.

08:23.670 --> 08:25.054
THESE CAMERAS
ARE JUST ONE TOOL

08:25.089 --> 08:27.398
FOR MAKING CONTACT
WITH THE SPIRITS

08:27.433 --> 08:29.707
AND FIGURING OUT
WHO IS ACTUALLY HERE.

08:31.244 --> 08:32.676
ADAM?

08:32.711 --> 08:33.645
I HEARD FOOTSTEPS.

08:33.679 --> 08:34.778
YOU DID?
OVER HERE?

08:34.813 --> 08:36.947
I HEARD LIKE TWO FOOTSTEPS,
LIKE, BOOM, BOOM.

08:36.982 --> 08:39.517
IT SOUNDED LIKE THEY WERE COMING
FROM THE UPSTAIRS HALLWAY.

08:39.518 --> 08:41.486
SOMETHING IS TRYING
TO REACH OUT TO US ALREADY,

08:41.522 --> 08:43.456
AND WE HAVEN'T EVEN
BEGUN TO INVESTIGATE.

08:43.491 --> 08:45.323
WE SHOULD FINISH
SETTING UP QUICKLY.

08:45.358 --> 08:46.724
IF THERE'S SOMEBODY HERE,

08:46.759 --> 08:49.428
THEY ARE GOING TO START
INTERACTING WITH US NOW.

08:49.463 --> 08:50.396
THEY'RE NOT GONNA WAIT.

08:57.236 --> 08:59.071
SO WE'RE GONNA START
WITH THE LIVING ROOM,

08:59.106 --> 09:00.404
FACING DOWN THE HALLWAY

09:00.439 --> 09:03.242
BECAUSE THAT'S WHERE THEY SAW
THE SHADOW FIGURES

09:03.277 --> 09:05.978
AND WHERE I HEARD
THE FOOTSTEPS.

09:06.013 --> 09:07.778
SO WHAT CAN WE...

09:07.813 --> 09:09.915
I MEAN, IF WE'RE LOOKING
FOR SHADOW FIGURES,

09:09.950 --> 09:11.181
WE'LL PUT
THE REM PODS DOWN.

09:11.216 --> 09:14.169
AND SOMETHING WALKS THROUGH,
IT WOULD GO OFF.

09:14.204 --> 09:17.122
WE USE REM PODS
TO POSSIBLY DETECT

09:17.157 --> 09:18.656
THE PRESENCE OF SPIRITS.

09:18.657 --> 09:19.958
LET'S PUT IT RIGHT
IN FRONT OF THE DOOR

09:19.993 --> 09:21.759
WHERE THEY SEE
THE SHADOWS.

09:21.794 --> 09:25.096
THEY PICK UP ON
ELECTROMAGNETIC FIELDS, OR EMF.

09:25.131 --> 09:26.530
PARANORMAL RESEARCHERS

09:26.565 --> 09:29.635
BELIEVE THAT SUDDEN
UNEXPLAINABLE CHANGES IN EMF

09:29.670 --> 09:31.337
COULD BE THE SIGN OF GHOSTS.

09:35.007 --> 09:35.973
ARE YOU READY?

09:35.974 --> 09:37.109
YEAH, I'M READY.

09:39.412 --> 09:43.582
WHEREVER YOU ARE IN THE HOUSE,
CAN YOU MAKE A NOISE

09:43.617 --> 09:45.785
SO WE KNOW YOU'RE HERE?

09:48.254 --> 09:51.123
IF YOU WALK BY THOSE THINGS
ON THE GROUND,

09:51.158 --> 09:54.491
THEY MIGHT GO OFF.

09:54.526 --> 09:57.512
CAN YOU WALK TOWARD US,
PLEASE?

09:57.547 --> 10:00.498
IS THERE ANYBODY
DOWN THERE?

10:02.467 --> 10:04.270
ARE YOU ERIC?

