DID YOU HEAR THAT?
A KNOCK.

10:55.921 --> 10:58.256
IT SOUNDED LIKE IT WAS
EITHER IN THE KITCHEN

10:58.291 --> 11:00.157
OR THE BACK BEDROOM.

11:00.192 --> 11:02.127
I THINK IT WAS COMING
FROM, LIKE, HERE.

11:02.162 --> 11:03.260
WASN'T IT?

11:03.295 --> 11:06.298
YEAH, MAYBE A LITTLE FURTHER
DOWN TO THE LEFT.

11:06.333 --> 11:07.298
THIS SIDE?

11:07.333 --> 11:09.867
YEAH,
THAT'S WHAT I THOUGHT.

11:09.868 --> 11:12.803
DO IT AGAIN.

11:12.838 --> 11:17.776
CAN YOU MAKE A NOISE
SO WE KNOW YOU'RE HERE?

11:20.946 --> 11:22.913
SO QUIET!

11:22.948 --> 11:24.449
LITTLE TINY KNOCK.
I DON'T --

11:24.450 --> 11:25.416
YEAH.

11:25.451 --> 11:26.784
IF THERE WERE MORE...

11:26.819 --> 11:28.971
MAYBE THEN IT WOULD'VE
BEEN SOMETHING.

11:29.006 --> 11:31.123
WE GOT ONE EMF SPIKE
AND ONE KNOCK

11:31.158 --> 11:32.789
SINCE WE'VE BEEN UPSTAIRS.

11:32.824 --> 11:34.593
AND ALTHOUGH THEY'RE BOTH
PROMISING SIGNS,

11:34.628 --> 11:36.326
EACH WAS SO BRIEF
THAT I'M NOT SURE

11:36.361 --> 11:40.564
WHATEVER'S HERE IS WILLING
TO COMMUNICATE WITH US.

11:40.599 --> 11:43.602
DISAPPOINTING BECAUSE I FEEL
LIKE THERE IS SOMETHING HERE.

11:43.637 --> 11:45.502
BUT MAYBE WE SHOULD
CHANGE OUR APPROACH

11:45.503 --> 11:46.872
AND HEAD DOWNSTAIRS.

11:52.644 --> 11:53.813
OKAY.

11:55.814 --> 11:58.048
HEY, ERIC.

11:58.083 --> 12:00.218
IF YOU'RE HERE,
MY NAME IS ADAM.

12:00.219 --> 12:03.354
HI. I'M AMY.

12:03.389 --> 12:07.593
YOUR FAMILY INVITED US HERE
TO TRY TO TALK TO YOU.

12:07.628 --> 12:09.994
I KNOW YOU MIGHT BE
A LITTLE SCARED RIGHT NOW

12:10.029 --> 12:15.367
BECAUSE MAYBE NO ONE'S
REALLY TALKED TO YOU LIKE THIS.

12:15.402 --> 12:17.303
BUT IT'S HARD FOR US
TO SEE YOU.

12:17.338 --> 12:19.170
