BUT WE HAVE THIS DEVICE HERE
IN HER HAND

12:21.525 --> 12:23.434
THAT IF YOU TALK LOUD
ENOUGH INTO IT,

12:23.469 --> 12:25.343
WE'RE GOING TO BE
ABLE TO HEAR YOU,

12:25.344 --> 12:27.713
AND THEY'RE NOT
GONNA HURT YOU.

12:27.748 --> 12:30.216
SO, ERIC, ARE YOU HERE?

