QUIET.

13:04.883 --> 13:07.051
WE MAY NEED TO CHANGE
OUR APPROACH.

13:07.086 --> 13:09.220
I THINK I'LL PUT THIS
IN HIS ROOM

13:09.221 --> 13:11.373
JUST BECAUSE THEN
IT'S FURTHER AWAY FROM US

13:11.408 --> 13:13.525
AND WAY LESS THREATENING
THAN HAVING US,

13:13.560 --> 13:15.259
LIKE, MAKE HIM APPROACH US.

13:15.294 --> 13:16.827
I'M GONNA FILM IT
WITH A FULL-SPECTRUM CAMERA.

13:16.862 --> 13:21.699
AND MAYBE IT'LL PICK UP
SOMETHING THAT WE'RE NOT SEEING.

13:21.700 --> 13:23.033
ALL RIGHT, ERIC.

13:23.068 --> 13:26.338
SO NOW YOU'RE IN THERE
IN YOUR SAFE PLACE.

13:26.373 --> 13:28.240
SO CAN YOU LET US
KNOW YOU'RE THERE?

13:28.275 --> 13:31.276
CAN YOU KNOCK FOR ME
LIKE THIS?

13:37.482 --> 13:40.151
IS THAT NOISE COMING
FROM THE BEDROOM?

13:40.186 --> 13:42.820
THAT SOUND
IS THE FULL-SPECTRUM...

13:42.821 --> 13:44.957
TRYING TO FOCUS
ON SOMETHING?

13:47.526 --> 13:49.127
WANT TO GO SEE WHAT'S GOING ON
WITH THE CAMERA?

13:49.128 --> 13:50.229
YEAH.

13:55.200 --> 13:56.366
THAT'S WEIRD.

13:56.401 --> 13:57.969
LET ME JUST
SEE WHY THIS...

13:58.004 --> 13:59.538
YEAH, WHAT IT
WAS FOCUSING ON.

13:59.573 --> 14:01.740
YEAH.

14:06.845 --> 14:10.180
I DON'T KNOW.

14:10.215 --> 14:12.382
I DON'T SEE ANYTHING
IN THIS VIDEO.

14:12.417 --> 14:15.220
SO EITHER THE CAMERA
IS PICKING UP ON SOMETHING

14:15.255 --> 14:16.420
THAT WE CAN'T SEE,

14:16.455 --> 14:18.856
OR SOMETHING
IS TOUCHING THE CAMERA.

14:18.891 --> 14:20.992
AND WE GOT NOTHING
ON THE RECORDER, EITHER.

14:20.993 --> 14:24.062
I DON'T KNOW HOW TO
GET HIM TO TRUST US.

14:24.097 --> 14:25.028
YEAH.

14:25.063 --> 14:26.230
ALL RIGHT.

14:26.265 --> 14:28.517
I FEEL LIKE WE NEED
TO SHIFT FOCUS.

14:28.552 --> 14:30.769
WHAT IF WE WANT
TO THE TABLE IN THERE

14:30.804 --> 14:32.237
AND JUST KIND OF
GAVE HIM SPACE?

14:32.272 --> 14:33.204
YEAH.

14:39.210 --> 14:40.443
IT WAS SO QUIET.

14:40.478 --> 14:42.046
AND I DON'T KNOW
THAT IT'S HIM.

14:42.047 --> 14:44.282
I DON'T KNOW THAT
HE'S READY TO TALK TO US.

14:44.317 --> 14:45.801
YOU KNOW, I FEEL
LIKE HE MIGHT HAVE

14:45.836 --> 14:47.762
SOME TRUST ISSUES
AT THIS POINT.

14:47.797 --> 14:49.653
I'M THINKING
THAT THIS IS A CASE

14:49.688 --> 14:52.958
THAT WE DEFINITELY NEED
TO HAVE THE FAMILY COME IN.

14:56.862 --> 14:58.829
I'VE CALLED IN
MY FRIEND CHRISTINE,

14:58.830 --> 15:00.866
WHO IS ANOTHER
PARANORMAL INVESTIGATOR.

15:00.901 --> 15:03.068
SHE DESIGNED
THIS HOLOGRAM DEVICE

15:03.103 --> 15:05.168
THAT CAN PRODUCE 3-D IMAGES.

15:05.203 --> 15:08.240
WE'RE HOPING THAT IT WILL
KIND OF BE A TRIGGER OBJECT,

15:08.275 --> 15:09.940
KIND OF ENTICE ENTITIES OUT

15:09.975 --> 15:12.511
AND HAVE THEM COME
INTERACT WITH US,

15:12.546 --> 15:15.012
WHETHER IT'S ERIC
OR SOMEONE ELSE.

15:15.047 --> 15:17.749
IT'S MADE USING
A REGULAR FLAT-SCREEN TV

15:17.784 --> 15:19.016
AND SOME PLEXIGLAS.

15:19.051 --> 15:20.969
AND AROUND IT
IS A PROXIMITY SENSOR,

15:21.004 --> 15:22.887
SO IF ANYTHING GOES
TOWARD THE HOLOGRAM,

15:22.922 --> 15:26.290
IT WILL SET OFF THE ALARM.

15:26.291 --> 15:28.994
WE'RE ALSO BRING SANDY
INTO THE INVESTIGATION.

15:29.029 --> 15:30.262
THANK YOU
FOR COMING OVER.

15:30.297 --> 15:31.461
GOOD TO SEE YOU.
COME ON IN.

15:31.496 --> 15:34.531
SHE'S SOMEONE WHO ERIC
WILL BE FAMILIAR WITH

15:34.532 --> 15:37.702
AND WHO HE WOULD FEEL
COMFORTABLE TALKING TO.

15:37.737 --> 15:39.237
THIS IS THE HOLOGRAM.

15:39.272 --> 15:40.703
AND IT FLIPS THROUGH.

15:40.738 --> 15:43.006
AND SO IT FEELS
LIKE YOU CAN,

15:43.041 --> 15:45.508
LIKE, REACH IN AND TOUCH IT,
YOU KNOW?

15:45.543 --> 15:48.914
OKAY, SO I THINK THAT THE BEST
THING FOR YOU TO DO

15:48.949 --> 15:51.149
IS TO BASICALLY
JUST KIND OF TALK TO ERIC.

15:51.184 --> 15:52.315
OKAY.

15:52.350 --> 15:56.221
LET HIM KNOW WHO WE ARE
AND THAT WE'RE SAFE.

15:56.256 --> 15:59.590
UM, ERIC,
IT'S ME, SANDY.

15:59.625 --> 16:01.927
THESE ARE MY FRIENDS
AMY AND ADAM.

16:01.962 --> 16:03.194
THEY'RE VERY NICE.

16:03.229 --> 16:04.262
HI.

16:04.263 --> 16:06.163
AND THEY'RE HERE
TO HELP YOU TALK TO US.

16:06.198 --> 16:10.935
SO IF THERE'S ANYTHING
YOU WANT TO SAY TO ME, MOM,

16:10.970 --> 16:12.905
THEY'RE THE PEOPLE
THAT WILL HELP US DO THAT.

16:12.940 --> 16:16.574
SO IT'S TOTALLY OKAY
TO TALK TO THEM.

16:20.078 --> 16:22.514
ERIC, ARE YOU HERE
WITH US?

16:27.419 --> 16:28.821
DO YOU LIKE THE HOLOGRAM
RIGHT HERE?

16:28.856 --> 16:30.454
IT'S A DINOSAUR.

16:30.489 --> 16:32.291
THAT'S PRETTY COOL,
RIGHT?

16:34.693 --> 16:38.530
YOU CAN ACTUALLY PUT YOUR HAND
IN HERE LIKE THIS.

16:38.565 --> 16:42.966
I'M GRABBING THE DINOSAUR.

16:43.001 --> 16:46.438
SO IF YOU'RE HERE,
CAN YOU LET US KNOW SOMEHOW?

16:46.473 --> 16:49.241
JUST TOUCH THE HOLOGRAM
OR SAY SOMETHING.

16:53.212 --> 16:55.814
WAS THAT YOU THAT USED
TO PLAY WITH ARIANNA,

16:55.849 --> 16:57.949
WHEN SHE WAS DOWN HERE
IN YOUR ROOM?

17:00.419 --> 17:02.053
DO YOU WANT TO LISTEN
TO THIS?

17:02.088 --> 17:03.922
YEAH,
LET'S LISTEN TO IT.

17:20.171 --> 17:21.874
WAIT.
WHAT IS THAT?

17:27.246 --> 17:28.746
IS THAT
WHAT WAS THAT WAS?

17:28.781 --> 17:29.715
YEAH, LISTEN.

17:32.651 --> 17:35.320
MY --

17:35.355 --> 17:37.054
CLEAR AS DAY.

17:37.055 --> 17:38.824
"WE HAVE TO TOUCH IT."

17:55.207 --> 17:57.008
- "WE HAVE TO TOUCH IT."
- "WE HAVE TO TOUCH IT."

17:57.043 --> 17:58.810
- "WE HAVE TO TOUCH IT."
- "WE HAVE TO TOUCH IT."

17:58.845 --> 18:02.246
IT'S LIKE THERE'S
MORE THAN ONE.

18:02.247 --> 18:04.499
ALL RIGHT.
LET'S KEEP TALKING, OKAY?

18:04.534 --> 18:06.752
SOUNDS LIKE
YOU'RE TALKING TO US.

18:09.554 --> 18:11.156
YOU SAID,
"WE NEED TO TOUCH IT."

18:11.191 --> 18:13.192
SO HOW MANY OF YOU ARE HERE?

18:15.460 --> 18:17.663
CAN YOU KNOCK
ON SOMETHING?

18:21.232 --> 18:22.366
LET'S LISTEN.

18:22.401 --> 18:23.869
<i> SOUNDS LIKE
YOU'RE TALKING TO US.</i>

18:33.212 --> 18:34.879
QUIET.

18:34.880 --> 18:36.413
UM, UNFORTUNATELY,

18:36.448 --> 18:39.217
WHOEVER THIS IS HAS STOPPED
COMMUNICATING WITH US.

18:39.252 --> 18:40.618
ALL RIGHT. YOU WANT TO GO UP
IN THE UPSTAIRS?

18:40.653 --> 18:41.919
- YEAH, LET'S DO IT.
- LET'S DO SOME THAT.

18:41.920 --> 18:44.456
NOW THAT WE KNOW THERE
ARE MULTIPLE ENTITIES HERE,

18:44.491 --> 18:46.022
WE'LL HAVE TO CAST A WIDER NET

18:46.057 --> 18:49.161
TO FIND OUT WHICH SPIRITS
WE'RE ACTUALLY DEALING WITH.

18:53.198 --> 18:54.932
THERE'S A LOT OF THINGS
GOING ON DOWNSTAIRS.

18:54.967 --> 18:56.501
IT'S SAYING,
"WE NEED TO TOUCH IT."

18:56.536 --> 18:57.700
THAT'S WEIRD!

18:57.735 --> 18:59.370
YEAH. AND THAT MEANS
IT'S MORE THAN ONE PERSON.

18:59.405 --> 19:00.906
AND WHO'S "WE" AND WHY?

19:00.941 --> 19:01.939
YEAH.

19:01.974 --> 19:04.960
STILL, I'M LEANING
TOWARD IT BEING ERIC.

19:04.995 --> 19:07.946
I DON'T SEE
ANYTHING CONCRETE, THOUGH.

19:07.981 --> 19:09.113
I DON'T HAVE ANY --

19:09.114 --> 19:12.150
TO ME, I DON'T FEEL LIKE
WE HAVE ENOUGH TO SAY,

19:12.185 --> 19:13.318
"THIS IS DEFINITELY ERIC."

19:13.353 --> 19:14.283
BUT WHO IS IT?

19:14.318 --> 19:15.752
ERIC COULD BE
ONE OF THE SPIRITS.

19:15.787 --> 19:18.506
BUT THERE HAS TO BE
SOMETHING ELSE HERE,

19:18.541 --> 19:21.226
EITHER ATTACHED TO THE LAND
OR THE HOUSE.

19:21.261 --> 19:22.458
AND A LOT OF STUFF

19:22.493 --> 19:25.363
WE HAVE GOTTEN
DOESN'T INDICATE

19:25.398 --> 19:28.198
A DEFINITE PERSON
OR AN IDENTITY.

19:28.233 --> 19:30.668
AND SO I THINK WE NEED TO DIG
DEEP INTO THE BASEMENT.

19:30.669 --> 19:33.138
I MEAN, SANDY'S DAUGHTER
AND HER GRANDDAUGHTER

19:33.173 --> 19:35.607
BOTH LIVED DOWN THERE
AND HAD EXPERIENCES.

19:35.642 --> 19:36.973
WE SHOULD TALK TO THEM,

19:37.008 --> 19:39.778
SEE IF THEY CAN DESCRIBE
WHAT THIS APPARITION LOOKS LIKE

19:39.813 --> 19:41.077
THAT THEY'VE EACH SEEN.

19:41.112 --> 19:43.913
AND COMPARE IT TO PHOTOGRAPHS,
ASK THE FAMILY,

19:43.948 --> 19:45.717
SEE IF WE CAN FIGURE OUT WHO IT
IS THAT WE'RE DEALING WITH.

19:45.752 --> 19:47.586
YEAH.

19:50.255 --> 19:52.224
TODAY I'M GOING TO MEET UP
WITH SANDY'S DAUGHTER

19:52.259 --> 19:54.326
AND GRANDDAUGHTER
TO GET MORE INFORMATION

19:54.361 --> 19:56.361
ON THAT FIGURE IN THE CLOSET.

19:59.397 --> 20:01.332
ALL RIGHT.

20:01.333 --> 20:03.334
SO YOU'RE ARIANNA?
IS THAT RIGHT?

20:03.369 --> 20:05.370
DO YOU GO BY ARI
OR ARIANNA?

20:05.405 --> 20:07.337
YOU CAN CALL ME WHATEVER.

20:07.372 --> 20:10.175
OKAY. NOW, THIS --
WAS THIS YOUR ROOM?

20:10.210 --> 20:11.408
- YEAH.
- YEAH?

20:11.409 --> 20:14.411
AND WHEN YOU WERE
IN THIS ROOM,

20:14.446 --> 20:16.380
DID YOU SEE SOMEBODY
IN YOUR CLOSET?

20:16.381 --> 20:19.685
WELL, UM...

20:20.986 --> 20:26.325
I SAW, LIKE, A MAN STANDING
RIGHT HERE IN MY ROOM.

20:28.926 --> 20:31.661
REALLY?
AND WHAT WAS HE DOING?

20:31.696 --> 20:35.867
HE WAS JUST LOOKING AT ME
LIKE IN A STRANGE AND EVIL WAY.

20:35.902 --> 20:39.087
SO HE WASN'T BEING
SILLY OR ANYTHING?

20:39.122 --> 20:42.238
NO? HE WAS JUST
STANDING STILL LIKE THAT?

20:42.273 --> 20:44.810
SO WHAT WOULD YOU DO?
HOW'D YOU MAKE HIM GO AWAY?

20:44.845 --> 20:46.610
I TURNED AROUND,
I GOT UP,

20:46.611 --> 20:48.513
AND THEN I SHUT THE DOOR.

20:48.548 --> 20:50.380
AND THEN I WENT
BACK TO BED.

20:50.415 --> 20:52.050
BUT THEN IN THE MIDDLE
OF THE NIGHT,

20:52.085 --> 20:54.418
IT WAS OPEN AGAIN.

20:54.453 --> 20:56.886
OKAY. AND HOW MANY TIMES
DID THAT HAPPEN?

20:56.921 --> 21:03.328
I SAW HIM LIKE FIVE TIMES
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE NIGHT.

21:04.863 --> 21:07.565
HOW LONG AGO WAS THIS
THAT THIS HAPPENED?

21:07.600 --> 21:08.932
THE FIRST TIME SHE TOLD ME

21:08.967 --> 21:10.466
IT WAS PROBABLY
ABOUT THREE YEARS AGO.

21:10.501 --> 21:12.235
OKAY. SO SHE WOULD'VE BEEN 4,
ABOUT THAT TIME?

21:12.236 --> 21:13.536
YES.

21:13.571 --> 21:15.139
WERE YOU SCARED?

21:15.140 --> 21:16.139
A LOT.

21:16.174 --> 21:17.675
YEAH? YOU REMEMBER
WHAT HE LOOKED LIKE?

21:17.710 --> 21:20.544
YEAH. HE WAS, LIKE,
HAVING --

21:20.579 --> 21:24.081
HAD, LIKE,
A WORK SHIRT ON AND A TIE.

21:24.082 --> 21:26.416
AND HE HAD A HAT.

21:26.451 --> 21:29.452
HE HAD, LIKE, BOOTS ON.

21:29.487 --> 21:32.691
AND THEY, LIKE, HAD,
LIKE, BUTTONS ON IT.

21:32.726 --> 21:34.390
OKAY.

21:34.425 --> 21:37.529
THERE IS A BIG DIFFERENCE
BETWEEN PARANORMAL

21:37.564 --> 21:40.282
AND IMAGINATION
WHEN IT COMES TO KIDS.

21:40.317 --> 21:42.966
AND IT'S TOUGH
TO GAUGE IT SOMETIMES.

21:43.001 --> 21:45.137
ARIANNA DESCRIBED
THE FIGURE IN HER CLOSET

21:45.172 --> 21:46.370
WITH SUCH DETAIL

21:46.371 --> 21:47.871
THAT I'M CALLING IN
A SKETCH ARTIST

21:47.906 --> 21:49.907
TO SEE IF WE CAN GET
SOME CONCRETE EVIDENCE

21:49.942 --> 21:51.810
AS TO WHO THIS FIGURE IS.

21:54.046 --> 21:57.416
I REMEMBER THAT
HIS HAIR WAS BROWN.

22:00.018 --> 22:02.386
HE WAS TALL.

22:02.421 --> 22:04.720
LONG PANTS ON.

22:04.755 --> 22:05.922
WHILE I'M DOING THAT,

22:05.957 --> 22:07.357
ADAM'S GOING TO
SIT DOWN WITH LINDA

22:07.392 --> 22:10.962
TO SEE WHAT MORE HE CAN
UNCOVER ABOUT ERIC.

22:10.997 --> 22:12.931
IS THIS, UM,
IS THIS ERIC?

22:12.966 --> 22:14.665
THAT'S ERIC, YEAH.

22:14.700 --> 22:16.333
AND HOW OLD WAS
HE IN THIS PICTURE?

22:16.368 --> 22:21.105
IN THAT PICTURE,
HE WAS, UM, LET ME SEE, 19, 20.

22:21.140 --> 22:23.674
OKAY. AND THEN
HE PASSED AT, UM...

22:23.709 --> 22:25.442
HE WAS 33.

22:25.477 --> 22:26.943
HE WAS VERY PROTECTIVE.

22:26.978 --> 22:28.511
AND THAT'S THE REASON
WHY HE WAS KILLED,

22:28.546 --> 22:32.150
WAS BECAUSE MY OTHER BROTHER
WAS USING A CROWBAR

22:32.185 --> 22:33.583
TO BREAK OPEN THE DOOR.

22:33.618 --> 22:35.552
THERE'S THIS TECHNIQUE
THAT WE USE

22:35.587 --> 22:38.724
WHERE WE TRY TO CAPTURE
ELECTRONIC VOICE PHENOMENA.

22:38.759 --> 22:42.258
WE ASK QUESTIONS,
AND WE DON'T HAVE YOU

22:42.293 --> 22:44.328
TO COME DOWNSTAIRS WITH US,
SO WHAT I WANT TO DO IS --

22:44.363 --> 22:47.565
I'D LOVE TO RECORD
YOU ASKING SOME QUESTIONS.

22:47.600 --> 22:48.664
OKAY.

22:48.699 --> 22:50.701
BECAUSE MAYBE YOUR VOICE,
THEY CAN HEAR IT,

22:50.736 --> 22:52.703
AND THEY'RE GONNA WANT
TO, LIKE, TALK TO US

22:52.738 --> 22:53.737
A LITTLE BIT MORE.
- OKAY.

22:53.772 --> 22:55.872
- I'LL START RECORDING NOW.
- OKAY.

22:55.907 --> 22:59.945
THIS IS ADAM WITH LINDA,
AND, WHOEVER'S LISTENING,

22:59.980 --> 23:01.945
SHE IS GOING TO ASK YOU
A FEW QUESTIONS.

23:01.980 --> 23:05.817
IF YOU COULD RESPOND,
THAT WOULD BE WONDERFUL.

23:05.852 --> 23:07.819
ERIC, ARE YOU HERE,
HONEY?

23:07.854 --> 23:09.585
I REALLY MISS YOU.

23:09.620 --> 23:13.556
I MISS OUR TIMES TOGETHER.

23:13.557 --> 23:15.591
WE MISS YOU VERY MUCH,

23:15.626 --> 23:20.281
AND IF YOU COULD GIVE US
ANY SIGN THAT YOU'RE OKAY

23:20.316 --> 23:24.936
AND THAT WE CAN ALL REST KNOWING
THAT YOU'RE FINE.

23:24.971 --> 23:26.705
WE LOVE YOU,
AND WE MISS YOU.

23:31.075 --> 23:32.008
THAT'S GREAT.

23:32.043 --> 23:34.277
IT CAN'T COME
FROM ANYONE BETTER.

23:34.278 --> 23:36.214
IF WE COULD LINK
ALL THE ACTIVITY TO ERIC,

23:36.249 --> 23:38.901
IT WOULD BE AN INCREDIBLE
RELIEF FOR LINDA.

23:38.936 --> 23:41.478
BUT WE KNOW THERE'S NOT
JUST ONE ENTITY HERE.

23:41.513 --> 23:44.021
SO WE REALLY NEED
TO IDENTIFY BOTH SPIRITS.

23:44.056 --> 23:46.890
AND HOPEFULLY,
AMY HAS SOME LEADS.

23:46.891 --> 23:48.825
WELL, I HAVE SKETCHES.

23:48.860 --> 23:52.062
THIS IS WHAT ARIANNA SAW
IN HER CLOSET IN HER ROOM.

23:52.063 --> 23:53.298
ARE YOU READY FOR THIS?

24:02.407 --> 24:04.941
WELL, I HAVE SKETCHES.

24:04.976 --> 24:08.179
THIS IS WHAT ARIANNA SAW
IN HER CLOSET IN HER ROOM.

24:08.214 --> 24:10.682
ARE YOU READY FOR THIS?

24:10.717 --> 24:12.301
THAT IS NOT ERIC.

24:12.336 --> 24:13.850
- REALLY?
- YEAH.

24:13.885 --> 24:16.686
THIS IS HIM WHEN
HE WAS IN SCHOOL.

24:16.721 --> 24:18.622
THIS DOESN'T FIT
THE DESCRIPTION OF ERIC,

24:18.657 --> 24:19.923
BY ANY STRETCH.

24:19.958 --> 24:21.424
NO. THE GLASSES,
THE HAIR, THE NOSE.

24:21.459 --> 24:24.395
YEAH. SHE SAID HE'S
VERY TALL AND SKINNY.

24:24.430 --> 24:27.664
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHO THIS IS.

24:27.699 --> 24:29.634
THERE IS ONE DETAIL
SHE TOLD ME, THOUGH,

24:29.669 --> 24:31.169
THAT I FOUND
REALLY INTERESTING.

24:31.204 --> 24:32.302
WHAT?

24:32.337 --> 24:36.458
SHE SAID THE BOOTS HE WORE
HAD BUTTONS ON THE SIDE.

24:36.493 --> 24:40.579
YEAH, AND SHE SAID DISTINCTLY,
LIKE, ON THE SIDE.

24:40.614 --> 24:44.249
SO I DID SOME RESEARCH
INTO, LIKE, FOOTWEAR.

24:44.284 --> 24:46.583
ONLY THING I CAN FIND
THAT MATCHES

24:46.618 --> 24:49.354
ARE BOOTS THAT MEN IN,
LIKE, THE EARLY 1900s.

24:49.389 --> 24:52.090
THERE WERE SOME BOOTS
THAT THEY WOULD'VE WORN

24:52.125 --> 24:53.523
THAT LOOKED LIKE THAT.

24:53.558 --> 24:55.226
I MEAN, AND THAT'S NOT
SOMETHING SHE WOULD'VE KNOWN,

24:55.261 --> 24:56.592
BEING 7.

24:56.627 --> 24:58.495
SO I'M GONNA LOOK INTO IT
A LITTLE BIT MORE.

24:58.496 --> 25:02.033
BUT THAT MIGHT GIVE US A CLUE
AS TO WHO MIGHT BE HERE.

25:04.836 --> 25:06.836
TODAY I'M HEADED
TO THE TOWN ARCHIVES

25:06.871 --> 25:09.407
TO SEE WHAT I CAN UNCOVER
ABOUT OUR MYSTERIOUS FIGURE

25:09.442 --> 25:10.806
IN THE BASEMENT CLOSET.

25:10.841 --> 25:12.543
SINCE MOST SPIRITS WE ENCOUNTER

25:12.578 --> 25:14.210
ARE VICTIMS OF A TRAGIC FATE,

25:14.245 --> 25:15.912
AND OUR SUSPECT APPEARS
TO HAVE LIVED

25:15.913 --> 25:17.547
IN THE EARLY 20th CENTURY,

25:17.582 --> 25:19.183
I'M GOING TO USE
THAT INFORMATION TO SEE

25:19.218 --> 25:21.620
IF I CAN IDENTIFY WHO HE WAS.

25:25.957 --> 25:26.891
I FOUND SOMETHING.

25:27.925 --> 25:30.061
IN 1908,
THERE WAS SOMETHING CALLED

25:30.096 --> 25:31.562
THE GREAT FIRE OF CHELSEA.

25:31.597 --> 25:33.263
AND IT WAS HUGE.

25:33.298 --> 25:34.265
I MEAN, I THINK
THERE WAS SOMETHING

25:34.300 --> 25:36.200
LIKE 85 PEOPLE
PRESUMED DEAD.

25:36.235 --> 25:37.901
GOD!

