THAT KIND OF --

39:00.205 --> 39:02.673
- "KAPOW!"
- YEAH.

39:02.708 --> 39:05.107
MY GOODNESS.

39:05.142 --> 39:06.710
THAT'S WHAT ERIC WOULD DO.

39:06.745 --> 39:07.678
REALLY?

39:10.447 --> 39:12.949
ARE YOU SERIOUS?
HE WOULD DO THAT?

39:12.984 --> 39:15.217
HE WOULD LINE HIS CARS UP.

39:15.252 --> 39:16.687
AND JUST LIKE
THE LITTLE KIDS, YOU KNOW,

39:16.722 --> 39:18.372
YOU GET THE OTHER CAR,
GO FAST.

39:18.407 --> 39:19.988
- BOOM, LIKE THAT.
- MY GOD.

39:20.023 --> 39:22.492
AND THAT'S EXACTLY
WHAT ERIC WOULD DO.

39:22.527 --> 39:24.927
WE ALSO TALKED
ABOUT DOLLAR BILLS.

39:24.962 --> 39:27.530
AND YOU SAID
THAT HE COUNTED MONEY IN ONES.

39:27.565 --> 39:29.567
- RIGHT.
- IF YOU WATCH HERE...

39:32.269 --> 39:36.138
- MY GOD.
- MY GOD.

39:36.139 --> 39:37.505
JUST THAT ONE DOLLAR BILL.

39:37.540 --> 39:39.009
SAYS, "IT'S OKAY.
THAT'S ENOUGH."

39:39.044 --> 39:40.342
AND IT STAYS DOWN.

39:40.377 --> 39:42.712
IT DOESN'T MOVE.

39:42.713 --> 39:44.315
LET'S SEE IT
ONE MORE TIME.

39:46.917 --> 39:48.401
MY GOODNESS.

39:48.436 --> 39:49.962
LIKE HE JUST WENT --

39:49.997 --> 39:51.453
YEAH, PUSHED IT DOWN.

39:51.488 --> 39:53.656
YEAH.
THAT'S DEFINITELY ERIC.

39:53.657 --> 39:54.858
DEFINITELY ERIC.

39:54.893 --> 39:55.891
YEAH.

39:55.926 --> 39:57.628
AND KNOWING AFTER
WHAT HE WENT THROUGH,

39:57.663 --> 40:00.929
THAT HE STILL HAS THAT IN HIM

40:00.964 --> 40:02.666
AND THAT MAKES ME FEEL
BETTER ABOUT THAT.

40:02.701 --> 40:05.434
GOOD.

40:05.469 --> 40:07.069
DO YOU FEEL
GOOD ENOUGH ABOUT IT

40:07.104 --> 40:11.274
TO MAYBE TO GO DOWN THERE
AND TALK TO HIM A LITTLE BIT?

40:11.275 --> 40:13.177
I HAVE TO GO
IN MY ROOM FOR A MINUTE.

40:13.212 --> 40:14.645
OKAY. YEAH.

40:21.018 --> 40:22.319
- IS SHE OKAY?
- SHE'LL BE ALL RIGHT.

40:22.354 --> 40:24.037
- OKAY.
- SHE'LL BE OKAY.

40:24.072 --> 40:25.721
UM, I'M JUST REALLY GLAD

40:25.722 --> 40:29.993
THAT WE WERE ABLE
TO GET ANSWERS.

40:30.028 --> 40:31.362
- I AM, TOO.
- AND VERIFY.

40:31.397 --> 40:32.328
AND VERIFY.

40:32.363 --> 40:33.529
I THINK THAT'S WHAT
SHE NEEDED.

40:33.564 --> 40:35.131
BECAUSE WE JUST DIDN'T
WANT HER TO BE AFRAID

40:35.166 --> 40:37.067
IN HER OWN HOUSE
ANYMORE.

40:39.069 --> 40:40.769
YOU ALL RIGHT?

40:40.804 --> 40:43.240
I'M JUST TRYING TO
COLLECT MY EMOTIONS, THAT'S ALL.

40:43.275 --> 40:44.475
I KNOW.

40:47.478 --> 40:49.180
I COULD TRY.

41:05.228 --> 41:07.164
YOU OKAY?

41:13.570 --> 41:16.572
SO MANY MEMORIES.

41:16.607 --> 41:19.441
THINK OF ALL
THE GOOD ONES.

41:19.476 --> 41:21.011
I HAVE TO THINK
OF THE GOOD ONES.

41:21.046 --> 41:22.244
ALL THE GOOD ONES.

41:22.279 --> 41:25.950
I GOT TO THINK OF THE BETTER
MEMORIES THERE WAS.

41:29.787 --> 41:33.290
ERIC, YOU'RE GONNA
GIVE ME STRENGTH TO CONTINUE,

41:33.325 --> 41:37.059
TO BE HERE AGAIN
IN OUR OWN HOME WITH YOU.

41:37.094 --> 41:40.497
WE'RE NOT GONNA LET ANYBODY
TAKE IT AWAY FROM US.

41:40.532 --> 41:43.451
I LOVE YOU,
AND I MISS YOU.

41:43.486 --> 41:46.079
I MISS OUR TIMES TOGETHER.

41:46.114 --> 41:48.672
I MISS EVERYTHING ABOUT YOU.

41:51.008 --> 41:55.011
I WISH YOU NEVER HAD TO GO
THROUGH WHAT YOU HAD TO DO.

41:55.012 --> 41:56.578
WASN'T FAIR.

41:56.613 --> 41:59.381
I WISH I WAS HERE
TO PROTECT YOU.

41:59.382 --> 42:02.719
BUT I KNOW YOU'RE GONNA BE
HERE TO PROTECT ME NOW.

42:02.754 --> 42:06.156
ERIC, I LOVE YOU.

42:06.191 --> 42:09.558
LOVE YOU SO MUCH.

42:09.559 --> 42:10.828
REALLY DO.

42:12.896 --> 42:16.300
I CAN'T HELP BUT GET
EMOTIONAL ON CASES LIKE THIS

42:16.335 --> 42:18.619
BECAUSE WE CAME IN
TO FIND A BROKEN WOMAN,

42:18.654 --> 42:20.904
AND WE WERE ABLE
TO GIVE HER SOME PEACE.

42:20.939 --> 42:21.803
YOU DID IT.

42:21.838 --> 42:24.057
YES, I DID IT.
THANK YOU.

42:24.092 --> 42:26.552
THANK YOU ALL SO MUCH.

42:26.587 --> 42:28.978
YOU'RE SO WELCOME.

42:29.013 --> 42:31.181
I DON'T THINK
I COULD'VE DONE IT ALONE.

